  {
    title: 'Gestión de Pedidos',
    description: 'Centraliza pedidos de Shopify y WooCommerce. Gestiona estados, pagos y canales desde un solo panel.',
    icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 10.5V6a3.75 3.75 0 10-7.5 0v4.5m11.356-1.993l1.263 12c.07.665-.45 1.243-1.119 1.243H4.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.12-1.243l1.264-12A1.125 1.125 0 015.513 7.5h12.974c.576 0 1.059.435 1.119 1.007zM8.625 10.5a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm7.5 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0z" />`,
  },
  {
    title: 'WhatsApp con IA',
    description: 'Chatbot inteligente que atiende clientes, detecta pedidos y escala a tu equipo automáticamente.',
    icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.625 12a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H8.25m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H12m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0h-.375M21 12c0 4.556-4.03 8.25-9 8.25a9.764 9.764 0 01-2.555-.337A5.972 5.972 0 015.41 20.97a5.969 5.969 0 01-.474-.065 4.48 4.48 0 00.978-2.025c.09-.457-.133-.901-.467-1.226C3.93 16.178 3 14.189 3 12c0-4.556 4.03-8.25 9-8.25s9 3.694 9 8.25z" />`,
